    "name": "英灵殿之子 Sons of Valhalla",
    "steam_appid": 1409830,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409830/extras/96a2fa53ac6cfece112a4c014fe37583.poster.avif?t=1767875913\" width=780 height=648 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409830/extras/96a2fa53ac6cfece112a4c014fe37583.webm?t=1767875913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409830/extras/96a2fa53ac6cfece112a4c014fe37583.mp4?t=1767875913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《英灵殿之子》將横版格斗与类rogue策略以及基地建造相结合，打造了一个精美的像素风维京世界，在游戏中，你扮演的勇士拉尔德・奥拉夫森，家园被毁、爱人被掳，誓要追捕逃亡英格兰的仇人酋长。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了报仇，你需要集结一支军队，亲自出征，在众神的凝视下，展开复仇传奇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409830/extras/b122c78ae2135bc7d0a3663c34b93368.avif?t=1767875913\" width=1560 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409830/extras/4829fb2f956eb2fffe5fe639fd333bb2.poster.avif?t=1767875913\" width=780 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409830/extras/4829fb2f956eb2fffe5fe639fd333bb2.webm?t=1767875913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409830/extras/4829fb2f956eb2fffe5fe639fd333bb2.mp4?t=1767875913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >远渡北海，背井离乡，追捕宿敌需要大量资源、兵力以及战略谋划。踏上英格兰乡间的征途，你必须选择前进的方向，管理有限的资金，与此同时浴血奋战、围攻城池、为装备讨价还价，过程中可以从故土召唤援兵，你所经之处横尸遍野。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >前面是多条岔路，后面是从北方席卷而来的狂风暴雨。你要穿梭于各个城镇，寻找商人、招募雇佣兵，从史诗般的攻城之战到旷野上的小规模冲突，免不了腥风血雨。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据你的战略需求，灵活折返、绕过或重返各个地区。在《英灵殿之子》中，之前经过的某个兴趣点（POI），你都可以再回去！曾经在军械匠那儿买不起的强力装备，你要回去看看吗？曾经让你望而却步的城堡，待你策略得当，扩充兵力，要回头一战吗？随着风暴逐渐笼罩大地，可能无法抵达远方的城镇，务必谨慎选择前进的路线。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战场上获取的资源可用于购置装备、提升部队实力，甚至建造建筑和攻城器械以推进你的征程。若暂时不用，这些资源还能在其他商人手中换取更强的力量。精打细算使用有限的物资，否则你的入侵行动可能很快就会宣告失败。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409830/extras/5bb41238ebf08860f5caea5ce69319e5.avif?t=1767875913\" width=1560 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409830/extras/3c8f9fc50e3d97ab63b0545989d0e1b3.poster.avif?t=1767875913\" width=780 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409830/extras/3c8f9fc50e3d97ab63b0545989d0e1b3.webm?t=1767875913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409830/extras/3c8f9fc50e3d97ab63b0545989d0e1b3.mp4?t=1767875913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战术战斗中，下达命令、运用特殊技能和阵型，领导你的部下歼敌。但请记住，真正的勇士会亲自上阵，所以准备好拔出你的剑，与兄弟们并肩作战吧。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >招募形形色色的部队与你并肩作战，你可选择普通的剑士和弓箭手，还有战斗铁匠、女盾牌手这样的独特勇士，每个部队各有千秋，要想在战斗中取胜，需要因地制宜，选对兵种。你会借助萨满的治疗能力让部队持久作战吗？还是更倾向于狂战士疾风骤雨般的挥击？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >指挥你的部队应对战场上瞬息万变的局势，命令他们排阵、冲锋、撤退，或是在箭如雨下时组成坚不可摧的盾墙。敏捷的思维、适当的站位以及不同的兵种搭配，在战斗中都起着关键作用。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >突破敌方的盾墙，用你手中的利刃将敌人斩落；或者掌握弓矛之术，在敌人靠近前就灭了他们。购置强大装备助你征战沙场，灌下蜂蜜酒来保持斗志，你要与你的士兵们并肩而立，掩护他们撤退，率领他们进攻。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409830/extras/ee2fd784ddb8f58c4b09fe861932db01.avif?t=1767875913\" width=1560 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409830/extras/0839a487840d9cf90498b92d5d639ef4.poster.avif?t=1767875913\" width=780 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409830/extras/0839a487840d9cf90498b92d5d639ef4.webm?t=1767875913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409830/extras/0839a487840d9cf90498b92d5d639ef4.mp4?t=1767875913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这场复仇之战中，你并非孤身一人。当你将英格兰大地燃为焦土，奥丁会从天庭赐予你力量，助你在战斗中所向披靡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗中你可以收集符石，献祭给奥丁，永久解锁强大的战士和装备，在后续战斗中可以利用。在《英灵殿之子》中，一旦战死，你将失去一切，不得不重新开启征途，但有了奥丁的庇佑，每一次重新尝试向着正义奋勇前行，你都会变得愈发强大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409830/extras/3cd3ad07b4147f6f2918ba68d9cc2a31.avif?t=1767875913\" width=1560 height=134 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409830/extras/b5566c60740996c2b64c562a5466cdf6.poster.avif?t=1767875913\" width=780 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409830/extras/b5566c60740996c2b64c562a5466cdf6.webm?t=1767875913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409830/extras/b5566c60740996c2b64c562a5466cdf6.mp4?t=1767875913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《英灵殿之子》的开发者是一对热爱像素艺术和维京时代的兄弟，在你征战与厮杀时，我们希望你也能尽情享受精心打造的细节，欣赏建筑的外观、水中嬉戏的鸭子、陪伴你的狗狗，还有昼夜交替、晴雨变幻间的整体氛围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409830/extras/780ef14505ff1bad4b9d2d7fd8a5708a.poster.avif?t=1767875913\" width=780 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409830/extras/780ef14505ff1bad4b9d2d7fd8a5708a.webm?t=1767875913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409830/extras/780ef14505ff1bad4b9d2d7fd8a5708a.mp4?t=1767875913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409830/extras/21af291721fb7e8121c14eb1ac8f4a2e.poster.avif?t=1767875913\" width=780 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409830/extras/21af291721fb7e8121c14eb1ac8f4a2e.webm?t=1767875913\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1409830/extras/21af291721fb7e8121c14eb1ac8f4a2e.mp4?t=1767875913\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
